  "detailed_description": "Enter the fantasy world and feel what it's like to be a real traveler! You woke up among ruins surrounded by a dense forest. You don't remember who you are or what you're doing here, so you embark on journey to find out.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2257870/extras/5ccbd885ec6757da20f5e8a68719f73c.poster.avif?t=1767918533\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2257870/extras/5ccbd885ec6757da20f5e8a68719f73c.webm?t=1767918533\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2257870/extras/5ccbd885ec6757da20f5e8a68719f73c.mp4?t=1767918533\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>You'll start making new friends - but also enemies. You will discover the truth about the local world and what secrets it hides.<br>Who knows what the future will be...<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2257870/extras/3ea65b0b8e90f1b284aa75f70f11d8f6.poster.avif?t=1767918533\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2257870/extras/3ea65b0b8e90f1b284aa75f70f11d8f6.webm?t=1767918533\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2257870/extras/3ea65b0b8e90f1b284aa75f70f11d8f6.mp4?t=1767918533\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>A Legend of Wisdom is a sci-fi platform game that requires strategic thinking.<br>You'll be casting spells, conquering peaks, crafting weapons, and arming yourself. You will face the greatest evil and free the world from power-hungry people.",
